steps.name: And I create a new Consignment note "Customer VAT payer"
Given I open hyperlink "e1cib/list/Document.ConsignmentNote"
Then "Consignment notes" window is opened
And I click the button named "FormCreate"
Then "Consignment note (create)" window is opened
If I see the attribute named "Organization" on the form Then
And I click Choice button of the field named "Counterparty"
And I go to line in "List" table
And I select current line in "List" table
And I set a car
Then "Consignment note (create) *" window is opened
And I click Choice button of the field named "Car"
Then "Vehicles" window is opened
And I go to line in "List" table
And I select current line in "List" table
And I expand the group named "TrailersGroup"
And I click Choice button of the field named "Trailer1"
Then "Vehicles" window is opened
And I go to line in "List" table
And I select current line in "List" table
And I select "30-Transport pe teritoriul naţional" exact value from the drop-down list named "OperationType"
And I select "101-Comercializare" exact value from the drop-down list named "OperationKind"
* Start place
And I click Choice button of the field named "RouteStartPlace"
Then "Locations" window is opened
And I go to line in "List" table
And I select current line in "List" table
* End place
And I click Choice button of the field named "RouteEndPlace"
Then "Locations" window is opened
And I go to line in "List" table
And I select current line in "List" table
And I click the button named "FormWrite"
And I check writing
And I click the button named "FormWrite"
Then user message window does not contain messages
* Documents list
And I move to the tab named "GroupGoods"
Then "Consignment note * dated *" window is opened
And I move to the tab named "GroupGoods"
And in the table "BaseDocuments" I click the button named "AddBaseDocument_SalesInvoice"
Then "Sales invoices" window is opened
And I go to the last line in "List" table
And I select current line in "List" table
And I activate field named "BaseDocumentsBasis" in "BaseDocuments" table
And I activate field named "GoodsProduct" in "Goods" table
And "BaseDocuments" table became equal by template
If number of "Goods" table lines is "more" "0" Then
And I go to the first line in "Goods" table
And I activate field named "GoodsNetWeight" in "Goods" table
And I select current line in "Goods" table
And I input "40,000" text in the field named "GoodsNetWeight" of "Goods" table
And I finish line editing in "Goods" table
And I move to the next attribute
And I select current line in "Goods" table
And I input "40,100" text in the field named "GoodsGrossWeight" of "Goods" table
And I finish line editing in "Goods" table
And I click the button named "FormWrite"
* Send to ANAF
And I click the button named "FormCommonCommandSendDocumentsToTaxOfficeETransport"
And Delay "10"
When TestClient log message contains 'Document Consignment note * dated * was sent successfully.' string by template
